title: The Complete Jillian Family Guy Timeline

media:group.media:title: The Complete Jillian Family Guy Timeline
media:group.media:description:
In this video we look at the entire timeline of Jillian from Family Guy. Created by Seth MacFarlane we look at Jillian's entire life story, her past and future. Taking a look at the Family Guy cutaways, as well as the full Family Guy episodes, I've put Jillian's life in chronological order. From season 1 to newest Family Guy season. I also go into the history of Jillian and Brian dating.

We also look at the funniest Family Guy moments from Peter, Lois, Chris, Meg, Stewie and Brian. As well as other Family Guy characters from Quahog Rhode Island.
